Privacy Policy
In all our apps, user data and activities are only saved on the device and never sent outside the device (even anonymously).
Note: Of course, you can export word lists or student activities by yourself.
Our apps don’t contain ads
External Links: Protected parent sections are available to send us an email, or view our others apps. Before accessing to a parent section, an addition or multiplication must be resolved so that young kids cannot access it.
Web site:  lescapadou.com does not collect user data